data.description: Welcome to this beautiful, lightly lived-in ranch style home in the desirable Tailholt subdivision! Featuring 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, the open floor plan allows for an abundance of natural light in the main living area. Kitchen features a large island, granite countertops, pantry, upgraded fixtures and cabinet pulls. Flooring has also been upgraded throughout the home. The primary suite is spacious with large windows, and the bathroom boasts dual sinks, a large walk-in closet, and oversized shower. In the backyard, the patio has been expanded to allow for additional entertaining space. All appliances stay, making this home move-in ready!
